<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Warrior on Balance Guides</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/tags/warrior/</link><description>Recent content in Warrior on Balance Guides</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 26 May 2025 18:00:59 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/tags/warrior/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Warrior Openers</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/tanks/warrior/openers/</link><pubDate>Mon, 26 May 2025 18:00:59 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/tanks/warrior/openers/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="warrior-openers-and-rotation">Warrior Openers and Rotation&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Warriors prepare their burst while waiting for the party buffs to appear.&lt;br>
After the buffs are up, fell cleaves are used first for comfort, but the order of IR GCDs can be swapped around as desired.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="opener-optimization">Opener Optimization&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Assumed Timings:&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Tomahawk starts at -0.70s and the pull starts at 0.00s&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Party buffs are expected to be up at around 7.80s, right when the first Inner Chaos goes out.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
